recordInEffectOn

public static <E extends HistoricalEvent> E recordInEffectOn(DateTime dateTime)
Returns the record in effect on the date/time required, i.e. the latest record with a date/time on or before that sought. Returns null if the date/time sought is before that of the earliest record.
